gin:0 0 4px 0;margin-bottom:4px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">If the button doesn&#x27;t work, paste this into your browser:</p><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:1.4;color:#cccccc;margin:0 0 24px 0;word-break:break-all;margin-bottom:24px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">https://unusonic.com/auth/verify?token=abc123</p><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Open the link on the same device you started from for the fastest sign-in.</p><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:1.5;color:#666666;margin:0 0 12px 0;margin-bottom:12px;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">If you didn&#x27;t request this, you can ignore this email. The link was sent to <!-- -->user@example.com<!-- -->.</p><hr style="width:100%;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eaeaea;border-color:#222222;margin:24px 0"/><p style="font-size:12px;line-height:24px;color:#444444;margin:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-top:0;margin-left:0;margin-right:0">Sent by Unusonic.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><!--/$--></body></html>"`;
